<h1>What do I do there?</h1>
<p>Treat yourself to a giant ice cream cone at Kimball's Farm, where Lisa used to go as a kid! Kimball's also has mini-golf, batting cages, bumper boats, and tons more.</p>

<p>Rent a canoe, kayak, or paddleboard from Nashoba Paddler and go on an adventure on the Nashua River! (note: Nashoba Paddler is cash/check only) </p>

<p>Go for a stroll in downtown Concord, where there are loads of shops, cafes, and restaurants.</p>

<p>Visit the adorable Alpacas at Luina Greine Farm!</p>

<p>Grab a pint at True West Brewing Company, or Rapscallion Tap Room.</p>

<p>Visit the Lowell Mill, about a 30 minute drive away.</p>